features: 📌【Long Handle】This dustpan broom combo features long handle design. The dustpan with handle height is about 118cm/43.3in; the broom with handle height is about 130cm/51.1in. 📌【30cm Broom Head】The broom features an extra wide 30cm broom head that is large for a larger cleaning area. And the bristles of broom are elastic that can effectively catch fine dust particles, pet hair and various detritus.

📌【Premium Material】This broom and dustpan set is made of premium stainless steel and plastic that is strong and durable. Lightweight and portable that is easy to use for various cleaning. Efficiently clean kitchen, home, office, lobby, etc.

📌【Efficient Cleaning】The broom features soft and elastic bristles design that is convenient and efficient to clean the corner trash and dusts. The elastic bristles will effectively catch fine dust particles, pet hair and various detritus. Efficient to clean the floor.
